item.title: Oregon’s Jordon Davison rushes 20-yard TD, extending lead over Wisconsin
item.description: Jordon Davison rushed a 20-yard touchdown, that extended the Oregon Ducks’ lead to 14-0 over the Wisconsin Badgers.

item.title: Vladdy Jr. Motivated by Guerrero Legacy, Compares Blue Jays to an Iconic Team
item.description: Vladimir Guerrero, Jr. tells FOX Sports' David "Big Papi" Ortiz about growing up in a MLB family and which iconic team reminds him of his Blue Jays.

item.title: Jordon Davison rushes for three-yard TD to give Oregon a 7-0 lead over Wisconsin
item.description: Jordon Davison rushed for a three-yard touchdown that gave the Oregon Ducks a 7-0 lead over the Wisconsin Badgers.

item.title: No. 11 BYU Extends Win Streak to 8 With Double-Digit Victory Over Iowa State
item.description: No. 11 BYU retained its perfect record and place atop the Big 12 after beating Iowa State by double digits on Saturday, 41-27.

item.title: Diego Pavia's Go-Ahead Touchdown Lifts No. 10 Vanderbilt Past No. 15 Missouri
item.description: Commodores QB Diego Pavia led his team to a win over Missouri on Saturday to extend Vanderbilt's best start since 1941.
